column2: SELECT TOP #   ROW_NUMBER() OVER(ORDER BY gi.specObjID) AS Row,   x.objID AS xObjID, gi.specObjID, gl.specObjID AS glSpecObjID FROM MyDB.FIRST_RADec_Half AS f   CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq(f.ra, f.dec, #) AS x   JOIN galSpecInfo gi ON x.objID = gi.specObjID   JOIN galSpecLine gl ON gi.specObjID = gl.specObjID
